sql:
SELECT name
FROM management_team
WHERE position = 'CEO' AND start_date > '2019-01-01';

external_knowledge:
Gross profit refers to the difference between total revenue and the cost of goods sold or cost of sales; 
The sector refers to a distinct group of companies that operate in the same or similar industry or market; 
Fiscal year refers to the financial year of a company, which may or may not be the same as the calendar year.

sql:
SELECT MAX(revenue) AS max_revenue
FROM company_financials
WHERE company_id = 1;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_press_releases
FROM press_releases
WHERE company_id = 0;

SELECT name
FROM companies
ORDER BY market_cap DESC;
